FBIS3-1211 "drafr056_e_94007" FBIS-AFR-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Mar 1994 WEST AFRICA Togo Bomb Explosion Reported Near Border With Ghana AB2203160194 London BBC World Service in English 1515 GMT 22 Mar 94 AB2203160194 London BBC World Service Language: English Article Type:BFN [From the "Focus on Africa" program] [Text] A powerful bomb explosion at dawn today completely razed to the ground premises of a popular drinking bar, Ataaso, in Lome only a few meters from the Togo-Ghana border. The bomb blast did a lot of damage to property and shook the adjacent houses to their very foundation, raising the specter of a bomb scare among the population.
